  11,47,"Nûh (Noah) said: "
  11,48,"It was said: "
  12,7,"Verily, in Yûsuf (Joseph) and his brethren, there were Ayât (proofs, evidence, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.) for those who ask."
  12,8,"When they said: "
